SPLICE METHOD

    splice is used to add new elements in the array from specifies to and from index
            let arr3 = [2,5,6,4,9];
            console.log(arr3)// [2, 5, 6, 4, 9]
            arr3.splice(1,3,"hii");
            console.log(arr3) //[2, 'hii', 9]
                Note: Elements from 1 to 3 (both ar inclusive )are replaced by hii

    splice can be used to delete the elements from the array.
                let arr4 = [14,2,3,5]
        arr4.splice(1,3);
        console.log(arr4) //[14]
